-- Gamco Fund Manager Haverty Says Google TV Is a `Marginal Product'
-- B y
-- 2010-10-07T01:23:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/gamco-s-haverty-says-google-tv-a-marginal-product-video.html
Larry Haverty, portfolio manager at 
Gamco Investors Inc., talks about Google Inc.'s TV service.   The service, debuting this month on Sony Corp. and Logitech
International SA devices, will include content from Time Warner 
Inc.'s HBO, General Electric Co.'s NBC, Netflix Inc. and Twitter
Inc. Haverty speaks with Susan Li on Bloomberg Television's 
"First Up." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:26